data.title: District: TCR: Details of Annual Income Submitted by Candidates
data.meta_description: 8_17 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides details of annual income submitted by 33 candidates from villages in the Chavakkadu Taluk of Thrissur district, including their name, application number, home address, annual income, and category. The incomes range from Rs. 24,000 to Rs. 267,000. The document lists personal information for candidates applying for entrance exams in Thrissur district.
